C.a4S=new Q.h("There are far more positions than you'd think in which a Pawn in hand makes a big difference. Look at Diagram 1.")
C.Hy=new S.I("7nl/5bgk1/5g1pp/4ppp2/7NP/4PB3/5P3/7R1/8L b P","Diagram 1")
C.a4d=new Q.h("White has formed a usual Yagura castle less one Silver. With Black's Knight on 2e, a Pawn drop on 3c will be quite effective. If you have a Pawn in hand, that is. Thus, a Pawn in hand could be compared to a thousand Gold pieces.")
