C.a_l=new N.a9(C.Ov,C.p)
C.a43=new Q.h("After Black's P*3c, White could play G-3a, but that would leave bad shape for White. So, Nx3c is a natural move, avoiding loss of material. Note the next move: Nx1c+. In the wrong direction, you say? No, this is right.")
C.a5V=new Q.h("There will follow:")
