C.a6x=new Q.h("By placing two Golds side by side to guard your King, you can buy time. In the yagura-opening, you are supposed to place your Gold on 6g, but when you get into the endgame, the Gold had better be on 6h for the defense.")
C.a1A=new Q.h("I might add that S-6h instead of G6g-6h is less preferable, even if it may appear to be similar in effect. There is a well-known endgame tesuji against the Yagura: S*6i, to which S-6h is hardly well-prepared.")
C.a44=new Q.h("Just remember that a Gold functions better when sitting in the back rank.")
