C.a6i=new Q.h("Diagram 1 shows White, who has already forfeited a Knight, has just dropped a Bishop on 8h. A daring move. Kx8h would only invite White to play Rx6i+, which would be too devastating for Black. When left unattended, White will play Bx9i+, promoting the Bishop on a very good square on top of taking a Lance.")
