C.a6A=new Q.h("The Rook is by far the most important piece in offence, therefore being close to the Rook means close to the battlefield. The King had better be some distance away.")
C.a3_=new Q.h("Thus, one of the basics is that you should castle your King in the opposite direction to your Rook.")
C.a2I=new Q.h("When you want to play the 4th file ranging Rook, begin with P7f, followed by P6f, and R6h. Then you go on to play K4h, K3h, and K2h, so that the Rook and the King sit left and right, safely apart.")
C.a2T=new Q.h("After that, you play S3h, G6i-5h, S7h. Now you have completed the Mino castle and about to be ready to move into the next phase. (Diagram 1)")
