C.a3y=new Q.h("Proceeding from the position in the diagram, Black will play P-4e, followed by Px4e, P-3e. Ideally Black should play K-8h or G-6h before opening the attack. Modern joseki teaches us, however, that procrastination is very costly in this position.")
